Check if an Array is Sorted
Problem Statement:
Write a Java function to check if a given array is sorted in ascending order.

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = {1,24,12,564,9};
        System.out.print(isSorted(arr));
    }
    public static boolean isSorted(int[] arr){
        for(int i=0;i<arr.length-1;i++){
            if(arr[i]>arr[i+1]){
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
}
